   "id": "md-title",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# BnB-WM: Set Cover Trajectory Collection **with Cutting Plane Decisions**\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook collects B&B trajectories from SCIP via Ecole and records:\n",
    "- Everything from the original collector (node bipartite observations, strong branching labels, dual bounds, leaf labels, depths)\n",
    "- **NEW**: Cutting plane decisions at each node\n",
    "  - `cut_features [n_cuts, 6]` — efficacy, violation, density, parallelism, obj_cutoff, support_frac\n",
    "  - `cut_labels [n_cuts]` — 1 if SCIP selected the cut AND it improved the LP bound, 0 otherwise\n",
    "  - `cut_lhs [n_cuts, n_vars]` — the actual cut coefficients (for CG cut propagation)\n",
    "  - `cut_rhs [n_cuts]` — RHS of each cut\n",
    "\n",
    "**Requires**: Ecole + PySCIPOpt (installed via condacolab below)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Output**: `.npz` files per trajectory saved to Google Drive"
   ]
  },
